node.text:
I filmed this clip with @treyshotya back in 2017.

A oral history of how I got a chance to work with my favorite artist and how he and @jermainedupri changed my life and we shifted the culture by redefining the ballad. From his self titled album to My Way to 8701 to Confessions, my brother @usher has been the GOAT.

Happy 20th Anniversary to 8701.

LOVE YOU BOTH @USHER + @JERMAINEDUPRI.

node.text:
Fellas,

Thank you for the proper life lessons and for your brotherhood. We have many milestones together but this one means the most to me. You guys accepted me in this creative space from day one and I will never take our relationship for granted.

BIG LOVE FOR MY NIGGAS.
@usher + @jermainedupri

Happy 20th Anniversary to 8701.

node.text:
I filmed this clip with @treyshotya back in 2017.

A oral history of how I got a chance to work with my favorite artist and how he and @jermainedupri changed my life and we shifted the culture by redefining the ballad. From his self titled album to My Way to 8701 to Confessions, my brother @usher has been the GOAT.

Happy 20th Anniversary to 8701.

LOVE YOU BOTH @USHER + @JERMAINEDUPRI.

node.text:
Happy Heavenly Birthday my brother, Scooby. LOVE! ❤️❤️❤️

This video always makes me happy.

Repost from @bryanmichaelcox
•
Cherish your youth.
Cherish your friends.

Love you and Miss you my brother.
Continue to rest well.

Happy birthday John Loray Caldwell aka “Scooby”.

📽: Young BMC.
